## Available Competitive Intelligence

- Competition description: `../research/description.md`
- 5 top kernel notebooks in `../research/kernels/`

data_findings.finding: Key approach: Use protein language model embeddings (ProtBERT 1024-dim, T5 1024-dim, ESM2 1280-dim) as features, then train MLP classifier on top for GO term prediction
Neural network architecture: 3-layer MLP with BatchNorm, ReLU, Dropout. Hidden dims like [864, 712]. Use BCELoss for multi-label classification with sigmoid output
Ensemble strategy: Combine deep learning predictions with BLAST-based predictions using weighted averaging. DL_WEIGHT and BLAST_WEIGHT parameters for tuning
